### Health Check
GET http://localhost:8000/health
Authorization: Bearer demo-cli:junior,senior,compliance

### Ingest Sample
POST http://localhost:8000/ingest
Authorization: Bearer demo-cli:junior,senior
Content-Type: multipart/form-data; boundary=boundary

--boundary
Content-Disposition: form-data; name=\"case_id\"

case-demo
--boundary
Content-Disposition: form-data; name=\"files\"; filename=\"sample.txt\"
Content-Type: text/plain

Case Note on Data Retention

Data Retention policies must follow GDPR requirements and ensure that personal data is deleted after the legal hold expires. The policy states that all client records should be reviewed annually to confirm compliance.

Additional retention guidance emphasises minimising personal data exposure.
--boundary--

### Ask Question
POST http://localhost:8000/ask
Authorization: Bearer demo-cli:senior
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "query": "Summarise the data retention duties",
  "case_id": "case-demo",
  "session_id": "demo-session"
}
